title: Spectrum Wall Planner
description:
The Spectrum Wall Planner is a poster-sized wall calendar with a new design inspired by the innate beauty of color. The Spectrum Wall Planner is open-dated so you can start using it at any time. Display page by page or all at once for a powerful long-term planning tool.
  • Dimensions: 30.1 x 20.6 in.
  • Materials: Environmentally friendly tree-free paper
  • 12-month calendar
